.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-BALANCE-SKEW" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-balance-skew \- FEAT-2172 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-balance-skew
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the average imbalance score across all peer channels (FEAT-2172).
.PP
Imbalance is computed as abs(local_pct - 50) for each channel and averaged.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
